name: test_addr_registration_deregistration[build]
description:
Submit registration and deregistration certificates in single TX.

        * create stake address registration cert
        * create stake address deregistration cert
        * register and deregister stake address in single TX
        * check that the balance for source address was correctly updated and that key deposit
          was not needed
        * (optional) check records in db-sync
descriptionHtml:
Submit registration and deregistration certificates in single TX.

    * create stake address registration cert
    * create stake address deregistration cert
    * register and deregister stake address in single TX
    * check that the balance for source address was correctly updated and that key deposit
      was not needed
    * (optional) check records in db-sync

labels.name: tag
labels.value: @pytest.mark.skipif(False, reason='cannot use `build` with cluster era 'alonzo' and TX era 'alonzo'')
